overview: My Trip to Miami follows a well-meaning, misguided, tourist as he tries to self-actualize via Trip Advisors algorithmic script. My Trip to Miami is a documentation of a fantasy, a failure in image-based expectations.
tagline: Wearing five GoPro's, Dylan attempts to visit, in five days, every one of Trip Advisor's "Top 315 Attractions in Miami'.
title: My Trip to Miami
